{
  "info": {
    "name": "Komands — APIM PRE VNO 03 Entel (Auto-Token)",
    "_postman_id": "komands-apim-pre-vno03-auto",
    "description": "Suite de integración contra APIM PRE-PROD — VNO 03 (Entel).\n\nCARACTERÍSTICAS:\n  • Token OAuth2 automático con caché — no se necesita ejecutar ningún request de token manualmente.\n  • 5 flujos: DeviceModification sync/async, Modification sync/async, Baja de Acceso.\n  • Assertions por campo en cada respuesta.\n  • Console.log con return_code y descripción para debug rápido.\n\nVARIABLES DE ENTORNO REQUERIDAS (importar VnoB1_vnoid03 PRE.postman_environment.json):\n  apimURL       — URL base del APIM (ej: https://epreapi.onnetfibra.cl/...)\n  consumerKey   — Consumer Key Axway\n  consumerSecret — Consumer Secret Axway\n  idvno         — ID del VNO (ej: 03)\n  accessId      — Access ID de prueba (ej: 03-TESTPREPROD-DIR02803674-1)\n  serial        — Número de serie ONT (ej: SCOM13032001)\n  speedPlan     — Plan de velocidad (ej: 940/940)\n\nEJECUCIÓN:\n  • Postman: Collection Runner → seleccionar esta colección + environment → Run\n  • Newman:  newman run \"Postman_APIM_VNO03_auto.postman_collection.json\" \\\n               -e \"VnoB1_vnoid03 PRE.postman_environment.json\" \\\n               --insecure -r cli,html --reporter-html-export reporte_apim.html",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{Token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ── Token OAuth2 con caché de sesión ──────────────────────────────────",
          "// Se ejecuta ANTES de cada request. Reutiliza el token si le quedan más",
          "// de 60 segundos; si no, obtiene uno nuevo de forma transparente.",
          "",
          "const expiresAt = pm.environment.get('_tokenExpiresAt');",
          "if (expiresAt && Date.now() < parseInt(expiresAt)) {",
          "    const secsLeft = Math.round((parseInt(expiresAt) - Date.now()) / 1000);",
          "    console.log('[Token] En caché — válido por ' + secsLeft + 's más');",
          "    return;",
          "}",
          "",
          "const apimURL = pm.environment.get('apimURL');",
          "const cKey    = pm.environment.get('consumerKey');",
          "const cSecret = pm.environment.get('consumerSecret');",
          "",
          "if (!apimURL || !cKey || !cSecret) {",
          "    console.error('[Token] ERROR: faltan variables apimURL, consumerKey o consumerSecret en el environment');",
          "    return;",
          "}",
          "",
          "const creds = btoa(cKey + ':' + cSecret);",
          "",
          "pm.sendRequest({",
          "    url: apimURL + '/token',",
          "    method: 'POST',",
          "    header: {",
          "        'Authorization': 'Basic ' + creds,",
          "        'Content-Type':  'application/x-www-form-urlencoded'",
          "    },",
          "    body: {",
          "        mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "        urlencoded: [{ key: 'grant_type', value: 'client_credentials' }]",
          "    }",
          "}, function(err, res) {",
          "    if (err) {",
          "        console.error('[Token] Error de red: ' + err);",
          "        return;",
          "    }",
          "    if (res.code !== 200) {",
          "        console.error('[Token] HTTP ' + res.code + ' — ' + res.text());",
          "        return;",
          "    }",
          "    const json = res.json();",
          "    const ttl  = json.expires_in || 3600;",
          "    pm.environment.set('Token', json.access_token);",
          "    pm.environment.set('_tokenExpiresAt', String(Date.now() + (ttl - 60) * 1000));",
          "    console.log('[Token] Nuevo token obtenido — expira en ' + ttl + 's');",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ── Guards globales de autenticación ──────────────────────────────────",
          "if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
          "    pm.test('AUTH FALLIDA (401) — token inválido o expirado', () => pm.expect.fail('HTTP 401'));",
          "}",
          "if (pm.response.code === 403) {",
          "    pm.test('ACCESO DENEGADO (403) — revisar permisos del consumer key', () => pm.expect.fail('HTTP 403'));",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 — DeviceModification Sincrónico",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('HTTP 200 o 202', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 202]);",
              "});",
              "",
              "const body = pm.response.json();",
              "",
              "pm.test('Respuesta tiene campo result', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('result');",
              "});",
              "",
              "if (body && body.result) {",
              "    pm.test('result.u_return_code presente', function () {",
              "        pm.expect(body.result).to.have.property('u_return_code');",
              "    });",
              "    pm.test('result.u_return_code_desc presente', function () {",
              "        pm.expect(body.result).to.have.property('u_return_code_desc');",
              "    });",
              "    console.log('[DevMod SYNC] rc=' + body.result.u_return_code + ' | ' + body.result.u_return_code_desc);",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{Token}}", "type": "string" }]
        },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept",       "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "vnoId",        "value": "{{idvno}}" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"u_id_vno\":        \"{{idvno}}\",\n  \"u_access_id_vno\": \"{{accessId}}\",\n  \"u_serial_number\": \"{{serial}}\"\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{apimURL}}/fullFillment-deviceModification/v1/deviceModification",
          "host": ["{{apimURL}}"],
          "path": ["fullFillment-deviceModification", "v1", "deviceModification"]
        },
        "description": "Cambio de ONT sincrónico. Requiere que el accessId esté provisionado en BluePlanet PRE-PROD.\nSi retorna 500, ONFNet debe activar el AccessID en el sistema."
      }
    },
